        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>This exhibit explores how the Industrial Revolution transformed our town from an agricultural community to an industrial hub in the late 1800s.</p>
        <img src="industrial_revolution_image.jpg" alt="Industrial Revolution" />
        <h3>Key Industries</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Textiles</li>
            <li>Manufacturing</li>
            <li>Mining</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Impact on Society</h3>
        <p>The influx of jobs led to significant population growth and urbanization in the area.</p>
